        <p data-uuid="7ae30f5660ab4164b7db13bb09444a6f">The time period in American history that Jackson‘s victory began is sometimes called the “Age of Jackson.” The new president dominated the nation’s affairs in large part because of his forceful personality and vigorous leadership style.</p>
